The,Agora,Interactive,Broadcasting,API,supports,the,integration,of,real,time,audio,and,video,streaming,functionality,in,web,and,mobile,applications,It,is,designed,to,facilitate,the,streaming,of,interactive,communication,discourses,such,as,live,broadcasting,and,group,audio,conversations,as,well,as,interpersonal,and,group,video,chats,The,cloud,based,API,is,accessible,through,the,Agora,SDK,features,WebRTC,compatibility,accommodates,up,to,seven,speakers,and,can,be,deployed,to,engage,large,audiences,numbering,as,many,as,participants,It,is,applicable,to,a,broad,spectrum,of,live,events,such,as,concerts,talk,shows,gaming,online,auctions,remote,personnel,training,and,online,classes,among,others